==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rescribe
<hw>Re*scribe"</hw> <pr>(r?-skr?b")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>rescribere</ets>; pref. <ets>re-</ets> re- + <ets>scribere</ets> to
write. See <er>Scribe</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To write back; to
write in reply.</def> <rj><au>Ayliffe.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To write over again.</def>
<rj><au>Howell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rescript</ent>⟦br⟧
